{"tid":1572372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"灣仔站被擲燃燒彈　港鐵稱未知能否周一重開","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T16:11:17.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1acf1ad96779584ed3597b5892e7bed817808f6a","tid":1572372,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"港鐵譴責激進示威者惡意破壞多個車站，指有人破壞站內設施，又向灣仔及銅鑼灣站投擲燃燒彈，港鐵表示已就破壞事件報警及保留追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n部分車站因受到嚴重破壞要暫時關閉，而遭到投擲燃燒彈的灣仔站，未知能否在明天早上重開，需視乎損毀程度及需要的復修時間。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵重申，關閉車站及容許警方入車站執法是為了保障乘客及員工安全，望大眾體諒。"},{"pid":"c1b69e21184baae4bbea53c92b9d812013753bd4","tid":1572372,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480736-20190915.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480736-20190915.htm&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=62422958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480736-20190915.htm&h=aa764d94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480736-20190915.htm</a>"},{"pid":"81ef70db54f038b5ec1e9dff798e9014e164624b","tid":1572372,"uid":278184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:11:17.000Z","msg":"最好一世都唔撚好開<br />\n執柒左佢啦屌你老母"}]}